RESPONSE_FORMAT.MARKUP:
Markdown with H2 for major sections, H3 for profile subsections;
    bold for key labels; no unnecessary headers inside the character
    profile itself.

METRIC.MEASUREMENT:
Character is not the most familiar version of their archetype;
      specific wound-motivation-flaw combination distinguishes them from genre
      default

Speech pattern is recognizable without dialogue tags;
      at least one specific verbal habit or register reflects the character's
      psychology
